OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some rain
OL,6,Fbut this will clear east during the
OL,7,Fmorning. The rest of the day will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but a few scattered showers
OL,9,Fwill develop, perhaps heavy in the
OL,10,Fafternoon over Buchan.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright end to the day with
OL,13,Fany showers dying out. Staying mainly
OL,14,Fdry overnight but cloud will increase
OL,15,Ffrom the west with a little light rain
OL,16,Fin places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
