OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny early light rain clearing
OL,6,Fthen a mainly dry and bright morning.
OL,7,FA cloudier afternoon with heavy
OL,8,Fshowers or longer spells of rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fsunny start to Wednesday then heavy
OL,13,Fshowers developing. Mainly dry and
OL,14,Fcloudy on Thursday, perhaps a little
OL,15,Frain later..Sunshine and showers
OL,16,Flikely on Friday.
